Republican Midwestern state, Lockhart kept pouring it on: ''In the
greatest American spirit of saving the best for last, he intends to
go to Nebraska before his term ends.''
</P>
<P>
   Lockhart dodged the next two questions -- Why has it taken him so
long? Does Clinton have something against Nebraska?
</P>
