of the week, played all 40 minutes of the game. But she struggled
offensively. Smith opened the night by missing her first three
shots and wound up with 10 points on 4-for-15 shooting.
</P>
<P>
   The Mercury avenged a 69-62 loss to Minnesota last Saturday in
Phoenix.
