   ATLANTA: RHP Kevin McGlinchy (sore right shoulder) threw off the
mound for the first time since going on the DL on May 24. He threw
about 60 percent and is hoping to pitch a couple of minor-league
rehab assignments by the end of the month. ... LHP Odalis Perez,
continuing rehab from a torn medial collateral ligament in his left
shoulder, threw off the mound for the first time since last August.
There is no timetable for his return, but it likely won't be until
next season.
