</P>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES: Entering Tueday's game, the Dodgers were 7-1 on the
road vs. teams from the NL Central, including 3-0 against the Reds,
2-0 vs. the Cubs and 2-1 vs. the Cardinals. ... With C Todd Hundley
playing, the Dodgers averaged 6.04 runs per game in 49 games. Since
he went on the DL May 31, they're averaging 4.44 runs a game.
</P>
